{"word":"ὀνειδισμός","slug":"ὀνειδισμός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ὀνειδισμός, οῦ, ὁ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ὀνειδίζω\">ὀνειδίζω</a></el>] ‘demeaning fault-finding’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in causative sense <b><a href='B:520 15:3'>Ro 15:3</a>; <a href='B:610 3:7'>1 Ti 3:7</a>; <a href='B:650 10:33'>Hb 10:33</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> in <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pass.\">pass.</a> sense <b>disgrace,</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ subj.\">subj.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a> <b><a href='B:650 13:13'>Hb 13:13</a>;</b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ w.\">w.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ obj.\">obj.</a> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ gen.\">gen.</a>, of Christ’s disgrace as experienced by others through association <b><a href='B:650 11:26'>11:26</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ὀνειδίζω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ὄνειδος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}